{
  "stem": "1775.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 216.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my husband decided he's going to go back to the lumberyard.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because for a while, he was working in the lumber yard there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they needed him because he knew what he was doing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he went back to the lumberyard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went with him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they had a group of people to go to dig turf.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They took me in there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I went, and I started to work on that river, digging turf.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was 1943, the end of May.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I worked at that from-- in the-- you know, the end of May, June, and July.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I worked there about close to three months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When all of a sudden, it was hell again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Three Germans got killed in our town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know who killed them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They said the Jews did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I don't know if the Jews did or the partisans did.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were sitting in a restaurant and eating, and they killed them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was in August.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "No, that was, I think, the end of July around-- I think the end of July.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when they killed those three Germans, naturally, the Jews did it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they took-- the Germans took-- there was a remnant of, legally, about a hundred people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the [NON-ENGLISH], they used to call them, that's the place where they used to get out all the Jewish stuff and pack it to send off to Germany.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they used to take all those-- and they used-- they took all those people that they were there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They dragged them-- five-- about four and half, five kilometers out of Miedzyrzec.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was a horse cemetery.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they killed them all there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And, and, and they left them for the Polacks to bury.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
